    {
      "id": "50fd6e14-c2f4-46b6-85dd-b4df36de7421",
      "type": "description",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit ${\\cal E}$ l'ellipse d'équations :\n$\\begin{cases}\\frac{x^2}{a^2} + \\frac{y^2}{b^2} = 1 \\cr\n        z = 0 \\cr\\end{cases}$\net $\\Omega = (x_0,y_0,z_0)$ avec $z_0 \\ne 0$.\nOn note $\\mathcal{C}$ le cône de sommet $\\Omega$ engendré par ${\\cal E}$.",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\({\\cal E}\\)</span> l’ellipse d’équations : <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\begin{cases}\\frac{x^2}{a^2} + \\frac{y^2}{b^2} = 1 \\cr\n        z = 0 \\cr\\end{cases}\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\Omega = (x_0,y_0,z_0)\\)</span> avec <span class=\"math inline\">\\(z_0 \\ne 0\\)</span>. On note <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\mathcal{C}\\)</span> le cône de sommet <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\Omega\\)</span> engendré par <span class=\"math inline\">\\({\\cal E}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "e2bf6f7e-5f84-44cd-a047-d56a4fa24b84",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Chercher une équation cartésienne de $\\mathcal{C}$.",
        "html": "<p>Chercher une équation cartésienne de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\mathcal{C}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "61da1866-0037-4e9a-8e0c-67fcbbf633bf",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$\\frac{(xz_0-x_0z)^2}{a^2} + \\frac{(yz_0-y_0z)^2}{b^2}\n              = (z-z_0)^2$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac{(xz_0-x_0z)^2}{a^2} + \\frac{(yz_0-y_0z)^2}{b^2}\n              = (z-z_0)^2\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "cbde4fe8-4e6d-4ef0-a8d6-0d93629a745b",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Quels sont les points $\\Omega$ tels que $\\mathcal{C} \\cap Oyz$ soit un cercle ?",
        "html": "<p>Quels sont les points <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\Omega\\)</span> tels que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\mathcal{C} \\cap Oyz\\)</span> soit un cercle ?</p>\n"
      }
    },
